OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782393517
OL,3,CE-scooter rider left with life-
OL,4,Cthreatening injuries after crash with
OL,5,Ctaxi
OL,7,FA 21-year-old man has been critically
OL,8,Finjured after the e-scooter he was
OL,9,Friding collided with a taxi in
OL,10,FBournemouth.
OL,12,FDorset Police received a report at
OL,13,F3.44am on Wednesday (24 June) of a
OL,14,Froad traffic collision on Wimborne
OL,15,FRoad, near to the junction with Talbot
OL,16,FRoad.
OL,18,FOfficers attended alongside the
OL,19,Fambulance service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
