PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782393517
OL,3,CE-scooter rider left with life-
OL,4,Cthreatening injuries after crash with
OL,5,Ctaxi
OL,7,FThe rider of the e-scooter, from
OL,8,FBournemouth, was taken to hospital
OL,9,Fwith injuries believed to be life-
OL,10,Fthreatening. His next of kin has been
OL,11,Finformed.
OL,13,FA road closure was put in place to
OL,14,Fallow for a detailed examination of
OL,15,Fthe scene to be carried out.
OL,17,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,18,For anyone with relevant dashcam
OL,19,Ffootage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
