CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782393517
OL,3,CE-scooter rider left with life-
OL,4,Cthreatening injuries after crash with
OL,5,Ctaxi
OL,7,FInspector Lee Turner, of the Roads
OL,8,FPolicing Team, said: "We are carrying
OL,9,Fout a thorough investigation to
OL,10,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,11,Fthis collision.
OL,13,F"I would urge anyone who witnessed the
OL,14,Fcollision or saw either vehicle
OL,15,Fimmediately prior to it and has not
OL,16,Fyet spoken to officers, to please get
OL,17,Fin touch with us.
OL,19,F"If you captured anything of relevance
OL,20,Fon dashcam, please also come forward.
OL,26,@pD@VOUuD@AOU
